message: I'd like to order some BBQ Pulled Beef

Great! I found BBQ Pulled Beef on our menu for AED 31.0. Would you like to place an order for this item? Please respond with 'yes' to confirm or 'no' to cancel. Additionally, I'll need a few more details from you:

- NYU ID (8 digits)
- Valid building number (options: A1A, A1B, A1C, A2A, A2B, A2C, A3, A4, A5A, A5B, A5C, A6A, A6B, A6C)
- Phone number
Yes I want to order. My NYU ID is 123 and my building number is A1A

Thank you for your order! To complete the process, could you please provide me with your valid phone number? Once received, we will process your order promptly. If you have any other questions or need assistance with anything else, feel free to ask. Enjoy your BBQ Pulled Beef at our dining hall!
Oh sorry for the typo, my NYU ID is 12345678 and my phone number is 123

Thank you for correcting that information. We've successfully received your NYU ID (12345678) and phone number (123). Your order for BBQ Pulled Beef (AED 31.0) has been confirmed. You will receive a confirmation shortly. If there are any changes or additional requests, feel free to contact us. Enjoy your meal!
